messageBody:
Enter your vote today! A new poll has been created for the
Read_Alphabet group:

Would you be willing to search your memory banks during October to think of a person who would be intrigued with the idea of learning QS and who would be willing to try a trial membership?

o Yes. Count me in.
o No thanks.


To vote, please visit the following web page:
http://groups.yahoo.com/group/Read_Alphabet/surveys?id=2342880

Note: Please do not reply to this message. Poll votes are
not collected via email. To vote, you must go to the Yahoo! Groups
web site listed above.

Thanks!
